Bestsport May Be Forced to Sell O2 Arena in Prague, CTK Reports

-- B y   L a d k a   B a u e r o v a
-- 
2011-06-29T06:00:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/bestsport-may-be-forced-to-sell-o2-arena-in-prague-ctk-reports.html
Bestsport AS, the operator of
 Prague ’s  O2 Arena , may soon be forced to sell the venue as part
of financial restructuring,  CTK  news service reported, citing a
decision by the company’s board of directors.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
